// ============================================================================
// SYSTEM SHAPE
//
// Flight Alert stays in one file deliberately, but former filename boundaries have no
// architectural authority. The foldable chapters below follow runtime flow: policy,
// domain truth, acquisition, safety, interaction, analysis, and drawing.
//
// The scaled-up Cistern rule is simple: keep control flow concrete and visible, give
// every concept one canonical implementation, and retain specialized hot paths when a
// generic abstraction would hide intent or cost measurable work.
// ============================================================================

